# Task 2 – Data Aggregation & Reporting with Real Dataset

This folder contains all `.sql` files and queries for **Task 2** of the SQL Practice Series.  
It focuses on advanced SQL techniques involving multi-table joins, aggregation, window functions, and data validation using the MySQL Employees Sample Database.

> ✅ Dataset Source: [DataCharmer/test_db](https://github.com/datacharmer/test_db)

---

## 📘 Topics Covered

1. Department Salary Summary  
2. Yearly Hiring Trends  
3. High-Earning Departments using `HAVING`  
4. Salary Distribution Report with Buckets  
5. Data Validation Checks  
6. Group-Level Filtering & Aggregation Logic  
7. Formatting & Output Presentation

---

## 🗃️ Dataset Used

**MySQL Employees Sample Database**  
Tables used: `employees`, `salaries`, `departments`, `dept_emp`

---

## 🛠️ Run Instructions

- Clone or import the [test_db](https://github.com/datacharmer/test_db) into your MySQL instance
- Run each `.sql` file inside this folder using **MySQL CLI** or **Workbench**
- Review outputs and take screenshots for validation
- Upload screenshots under the `task2screenshots/` folder

---

